"c38a (Little Spider)"

Photography + PLY File Databending, 2018. Source image captured in Northampton, Massachusetts. "[My ] Synthetic Autumn" began in 2015 as a project speculating what a transhuman ecology would look like during autumn in Western Massachusetts, once technological interventions become necessary to keep natural processes from collapsing. 

// Artwork by Sabato Visconti // This special NFT drop is part of the Florence Night Out Pop-up Exhibition at Pivot Media in Florence, Massachusetts, September 25. This exhibit marks 10 years of creating glitch art // www.sabatobox.com // @sabatobox on IG //
